trans-unit.source: Provides a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> class is a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects, typically used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object to manage a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects for a connection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> 클래스는 컬렉션의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> 일반적으로 사용 되는 개체는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> 개체 집합을 관리할 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> 연결에 대 한 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The transformers related to a Web Parts connection can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.Transformers%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 연결 관련는 변환기를 통해 검색할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.Transformers%2A> 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" /> class.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> to be added to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" />.
Adds an object to the end of the collection.
The index at which <paramref name="transformer" /> has been added.
A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 있는지 여부를 확인하기 위해 검사할 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular transformer exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 특정 변환기가 컬렉션에 있는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular transformer is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 특정 변환기가 컬렉션에 있는지 여부를 나타내는 부울 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.Contains%2A> method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> object and determine whether it is part of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.Contains%2A> 메서드를 사용 하면 특정 확인 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> 개체의 일부 인지 확인 하 고는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: An array of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects to contain the copied collection.
The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: 배열에서 컬렉션 내용이 배치될 시작 지점입니다.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.CopyTo%2A> method is useful when you want to assemble a custom array that can contain all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> collection, a subset of those objects, or a superset of those objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.CopyTo%2A> 메서드는 모두 포함 될 수 있는 사용자 지정 배열을 어셈블하는 데는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> 개체에 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> 컬렉션, 해당 개체의 하위 집합 또는 해당 개체의 상위 집합입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> that is a member of the collection.
Returns the position of a particular member in the collection.
An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 특정 개체의 위치를 나타내는 정수입니다.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which a value should be inserted.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> to insert.
Inserts a transformer into the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" /> collection at the specified index.
Gets a value indicating whether the collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션이 읽기 전용인지를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the collection and its items cannot be changed; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션과 해당 항목을 변경할 수 없으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The index of a particular <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> in a collection.
Returns a member of the collection based on its position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서의 위치를 기준으로 컬렉션의 멤버를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> located at <paramref name="index" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> to remove from the collection.
Removes the first occurrence of a specific transformer.
trans-unit.target: 맨 처음 발견되는 특정 변환기를 제거합니다.
